snippet.title: Longplay of Mega Man X: Command Mission (1/2)
snippet.description:
Longplay of Mega Man X: Command Mission, played as the NTSC version on the GameCube. This game's version was released on Sep. 21st, 2004. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Part (2/2): https://youtu.be/q79TKeVe8Bw

6:13:36 - Intermission Chapter 5-6
